// Get Params
function getQueryParams(qs) {
    qs = qs.split("+").join(" ");
    var params = {},
        tokens,
        re = /[?&]?([^=]+)=([^&]*)/g;
		
    while (tokens = re.exec(qs)) {
        params[decodeURIComponent(tokens[1])]
            = decodeURIComponent(tokens[2]);
    }
	
    return params;
}
var $_GET = getQueryParams(document.location.search);

<!-- SAFKOY TAG YONETIMI -->
<script>
// Page Type
var skPageType;

if ($_GET.do) { 
	switch ($_GET.do) {
		case 'static/contactus': skPageType = 'contact'; break;	
		case 'static/redir': skPageType = 'other'; break;
		case 'members/login': skPageType = 'login'; break;
		case 'members/login2': skPageType = 'login'; break;
		case 'members/signup': skPageType = 'register'; break;
		case 'catalog/product': skPageType = 'product'; break;
		case 'catalog/results': skPageType = 'search'; break;
		case 'catalog/order': skPageType = 'cart'; break;
		case 'catalog/order2': skPageType = 'cart'; break;
		case 'catalog/order3': skPageType = 'cart'; break;
		case 'catalog/order4': skPageType = 'cart'; break;
		case 'catalog/orderFinished': skPageType = 'purchase'; break;	
	}
}	
else {
	switch (document.title.split('-').last()) {
		case ' Anasayfa': skPageType = 'home'; break;
		case ' Ürün': skPageType = 'product'; break;
		case ' Kategori': skPageType = 'category'; break;
		default: skPageType = 'other'; break;
	}
}

// proid & total value
var skProdId = [];
var skTotalValue;
var tmp;
if ( skPageType == 'product' ) { skProdId = jQuery('#pid').attr('value'); skTotalValue = jQuery('span[itemprop="price"]').text().split(' ')[0].replace('.', '').replace(',', '') / 100; }
else if  ( skPageType == 'cart' ) {
	jQuery('[src^=modules]').each( function( index, element ){
		tmp = jQuery( this ).attr('src').split('_')[2];
		skProdId.push(tmp); 
	});
	skTotalValue = jQuery('._orderTotalCol2').last().text().split(' ')[0].replace('.', '').replace(',', '') / 100;
}
else { skProdId = ''; skTotalValue = ''; }
</script>

<!-- Google Remarketing -->	
<script type="text/javascript">
var google_tag_params = {
ecomm_prodid: skProdId,
ecomm_pagetype: skPageType,
ecomm_totalvalue: skTotalValue,
};
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
/* <![CDATA[ */
var google_conversion_id = 981429862;
var google_custom_params = window.google_tag_params;
var google_remarketing_only = true;

function skBadges() {
	var items = jQuery('.showcase');
	jQuery.each(items, function( key, value ) {
		// Ücretsiz Kargo
		if (parseInt(jQuery(this).children('.showcaseItem').children('.showcasePrice').text().split(',')[0]) > 30) {
			jQuery(this).children('.showcaseImage').prepend('<div class="cargoBadge _positionAbsolute"></div>')
		}
	});
}

function skHashChange() { setTimeout(function(){skBadges();}, 1000);}

if ((skPageType == 'home') || (skPageType == 'category')) { jQuery(window).load(skBadges()); }	
if (skPageType == 'category') { window.onhashchange = skHashChange; }
if ((skPageType == 'product') && (skTotalValue > 30)) { jQuery('.productLeft').append('<div class="cargoBadge"></div>') }

	function SimpleHash() {
		this.keys = new Array();
		this.values = new Array();
	}
	
	SimpleHash.prototype.put = function(key,value) {
		var index = this.find(key);
		if(index<0) {
			index = this.keys.length;
		}
		this.keys[index] = key;
		this.values[index] = value;
	}
	
	SimpleHash.prototype.find = function(key) {
		for(var i=0;i<this.keys.length;i++) {
			if(this.keys[i] == key) {
				return i;
			}
		}
		return -1;
	}
	
	SimpleHash.prototype.get = function(key) {
		var index = this.find(key);
		if(index>=0) {
			return this.values[index];
		}
		return false;
	}
	
	var PLXSuccessList = new SimpleHash();	
	
	function PHPLiveX(type, target, mode, preload, method){
		this.TYPE = type;
		this.MODE = mode;
		this.TARGET = target;
		this.PRELOAD = preload;
		this.METHOD = method;
	}

	PHPLiveX.prototype.ShowError = function(errorMsg){
		if(errorMsg != ""){
			alert(errorMsg);
			return false;
		}else{
			return true;
		}
	}

	PHPLiveX.prototype.GetXmlHttp = function(){
		objXmlHttp = false;
        if (window.XMLHttpRequest) {
            objXmlHttp = new XMLHttpRequest();
            if (objXmlHttp.overrideMimeType) {
                objXmlHttp.overrideMimeType('text/xml');
            }
        } else if (window.ActiveXObject) {
            try {
                objXmlHttp = new ActiveXObject("Msxml2.XMLHTTP");
            } catch (e) {
                try {
                    objXmlHttp = new ActiveXObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP");
                } catch (e) {}
            }
        }

        if (!objXmlHttp) {
            alert('Giving up :( Cannot create an XMLHTTP instance');
            return false;
        }

		return objXmlHttp;
	}

	PHPLiveX.prototype.CreatePreloading = function(preloadId){
		document.getElementById(preloadId).style.display = "block";
	}

	PHPLiveX.prototype.CreateOutput = function(funcName, funcArgs, funcUrl){
		var data = "funcName=" + escape(funcName);
		var args = new Array();
		if(funcUrl == null){ 
            funcUrl = decodeURIComponent("/index.php"); 
        }
		if(funcArgs != ""){
			if(funcArgs.indexOf(",") != -1){
				args = funcArgs.split(",");
				for (i=0;i<args.length;i++) data += "&funcArgs[]=" + escape(args[i]);
			}else{
				data += "&funcArgs[]=" + escape(funcArgs);
			}
		}
		data+="&anticsrf=8931007a25a4bec2316c5d70777ccf99e38601c3";
		
		var parentObject = this;

		var XmlHttp = this.GetXmlHttp();
		var ajaxType = false;
		if(this.TYPE != "r") ajaxType = true;
        
		if(this.METHOD == "get"){
			if(funcUrl.indexOf("?") != -1){
				XmlHttp.open("GET", funcUrl + "&" + (data), ajaxType);
			}else{
				XmlHttp.open("GET", funcUrl + "?" + (data), ajaxType);
			}
		}else{
			if(funcUrl.indexOf("?") != -1){
				XmlHttp.open("post", funcUrl + "&tm=" + new Date().getTime(), ajaxType);
			}else{
				XmlHttp.open("post", funcUrl + "?tm=" + new Date().getTime(), ajaxType);
			}
		}

		XmlHttp.setRequestHeader("Method", this.METHOD + " " + funcUrl + " HTTP/1.1");
		XmlHttp.setRequestHeader("Content-Type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded;charset=iso-8859-9");
		XmlHttp.setRequestHeader("Pragma", "no-cache");
		XmlHttp.setRequestHeader("Cache-Control", "must-revalidate");
		XmlHttp.setRequestHeader("Cache-Control", "no-cache");
		XmlHttp.setRequestHeader("Cache-Control", "no-store");
		XmlHttp.setRequestHeader("X-Requested-With", "XMLHttpRequest");

		if(this.TYPE != "r"){
			if(this.PRELOAD != null){ this.CreatePreloading(this.PRELOAD); }

			XmlHttp.onreadystatechange = function(){
				if(XmlHttp.readyState == 0){
					XmlHttp.abort();
					if(parentObject.PRELOAD != null){
						document.getElementById(parentObject.PRELOAD).style.display = "none";
					}
				}else if(XmlHttp.readyState == 4){
                    var output = (XmlHttp.responseText).replace(/%/g,"{~Yuzde~}");
					output = unescape(output);
                    output = (XmlHttp.responseText).replace(/{~Yuzde~}/g,"%");
					var outparts = output.split("<phplivex>");
					output = outparts[outparts.length-1].split("</phplivex>")[0];
					output = output.replace(/<plus>/g, "+");
					output = output.replace(/<comma>/g, ",");

					if(parentObject.PRELOAD != null){
						document.getElementById(parentObject.PRELOAD).style.display = "none";
                        setTimeout("ChangeCheckBoxStyle()",0.01);
                        setTimeout("ChangeRadioBoxStyle()",0.01);
                        setTimeout("jQuery('.tooltipOptional').tooltip()",1);
                        setTimeout("jQuery('.tooltipImage').tooltip()",1);
					}

					if(parentObject.TYPE == "e"){ 
						onSuccess = PLXSuccessList.get(funcName);
												if(onSuccess) {
							eval(unescape(onSuccess));
						}
						return; 
					}
					else if(parentObject.TARGET == "alert"){
						alert(output); 
					}
					else if(parentObject.MODE == "aw"){ 
						if(!document.getElementById(parentObject.TARGET)){
							alert('Cannot find HTML element:' + parentObject.TARGET)
							return false
						}
						document.getElementById(parentObject.TARGET).innerHTML += output; 
					}
					else if(parentObject.MODE == "rw"){ 
						if(!document.getElementById(parentObject.TARGET)){
							alert('Cannot find HTML element:' + parentObject.TARGET)
							return false
						}
						document.getElementById(parentObject.TARGET).innerHTML = output; 
					}
					onSuccess = PLXSuccessList.get(funcName);
										if(onSuccess) {
						eval(unescape(onSuccess));
					}
				}
			}
			if(this.METHOD == "get"){ XmlHttp.send(null); }
			else{ XmlHttp.send(data); }
		}else{
			if(this.METHOD == "get"){ XmlHttp.send(null); }
			else{ XmlHttp.send(data); }
			var output = unescape(XmlHttp.responseText);
			var outparts = output.split("<phplivex>");
			output = outparts[outparts.length-1].split("</phplivex>")[0];
			output = output.replace(/<plus>/g, "+");
			output = output.replace(/<comma>/g, ",");
			return output;
		}
	}

	
	function Add2Maillist() {
		var args = new Array(); var plx_args = new Array();
		var plxType = "e"; var plxTarget = null;
		var plxMode = "rw"; var plxPreload = null;
		var plxMethod = "post";

		for(i=0;i<Add2Maillist.arguments.length;i++){
			args[i] = Add2Maillist.arguments[i];
		}
		if(args[args.length-1].indexOf(",") != -1){ plx_args = args[args.length-1].split(","); }
		else{ plx_args[0] = args[args.length-1]; }

		for(i=0;i<plx_args.length;i++){
			if(plx_args[i].indexOf("type=") != -1){
				plxType = plx_args[i].substr(5);
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("target=") != -1){
				plxTarget = plx_args[i].substr(7);
				plxType = "print";
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("mode=") != -1){
				plxMode = plx_args[i].substr(5);
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("preload=") != -1){
				plxPreload = plx_args[i].substr(8);
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("method=") != -1){
				plxMethod = plx_args[i].substr(7);
			}
		}

		args.splice(args.length-1, 1);
		var FuncArgs = args.join();

		var PLX_Add2Maillist = new PHPLiveX(plxType, plxTarget, plxMode, plxPreload, plxMethod);

		try{
			if(plxType == "r"){
				return PLX_Add2Maillist.CreateOutput("Add2Maillist", FuncArgs);
			}else{
				PLX_Add2Maillist.CreateOutput("Add2Maillist", FuncArgs);
			}
		}catch(ex){
			PLX_Add2Maillist.ShowError(ex);
		}

	}
	
	function SaveCart() {
		var args = new Array(); var plx_args = new Array();
		var plxType = "e"; var plxTarget = null;
		var plxMode = "rw"; var plxPreload = null;
		var plxMethod = "post";

		for(i=0;i<SaveCart.arguments.length;i++){
			args[i] = SaveCart.arguments[i];
		}
		if(args[args.length-1].indexOf(",") != -1){ plx_args = args[args.length-1].split(","); }
		else{ plx_args[0] = args[args.length-1]; }

		for(i=0;i<plx_args.length;i++){
			if(plx_args[i].indexOf("type=") != -1){
				plxType = plx_args[i].substr(5);
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("target=") != -1){
				plxTarget = plx_args[i].substr(7);
				plxType = "print";
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("mode=") != -1){
				plxMode = plx_args[i].substr(5);
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("preload=") != -1){
				plxPreload = plx_args[i].substr(8);
			}else if(plx_args[i].indexOf("method=") != -1){
				plxMethod = plx_args[i].substr(7);
			}
		}

		args.splice(args.length-1, 1);
		var FuncArgs = args.join();

		var PLX_SaveCart = new PHPLiveX(plxType, plxTarget, plxMode, plxPreload, plxMethod);

		try{
			if(plxType == "r"){
				return PLX_SaveCart.CreateOutput("SaveCart", FuncArgs);
			}else{
				PLX_SaveCart.CreateOutput("SaveCart", FuncArgs);
			}
		}catch(ex){
			PLX_SaveCart.ShowError(ex);
		}

	}
